{"content":[{"data":{"color":"black","source":"The Narrator","time_period":["0s AD"],"unique_sources":["Paul"]},"nodes":[{"type":"prose","nodes":[{"marks":[{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"chapter"}],"object":"leaf","text":"8"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"1"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Now I want you to know, dear brothers and sisters,* what God in his kindness has done through the churches in Macedonia. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"2"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"2"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"2"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"They are being tested by many troubles, and they are very poor. But they are also filled with abundant joy, which has overflowed in rich generosity. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"3"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"3"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"3"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"For I can testify that they gave not only what they could afford, but far more. And they did it of their own free will. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"4"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"4"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"4"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"They begged us again and again for the privilege of sharing in the gift for the believers in Jerusalem.* "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"5"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"5"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"5"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"They even did more than we had hoped, for their first action was to give themselves to the Lord and to us, just as God wanted them to do. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"6"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"6"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"6"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"So we have urged Titus, who encouraged your giving in the first place, to return to you and encourage you to finish this ministry of giving. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"7"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"7"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"7"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Since you excel in so many ways—in your faith, your gifted speakers, your knowledge, your enthusiasm, and your love from us*—I want you to excel also in this gracious act of giving. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"8"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"8"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"8"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"I am not commanding you to do this. But I am testing how genuine your love is by comparing it with the eagerness of the other churches. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"9"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"9"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"9"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"You know the generous grace of our Lord Jesus Christ. Though he was rich, yet for your sakes he became poor, so that by his poverty he could make you rich. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"10"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"10"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"10"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Here is my advice: It would be good for you to finish what you started a year ago. Last year you were the first who wanted to give, and you were the first to begin doing it. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"11"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"11"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"11"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Now you should finish what you started. Let the eagerness you showed in the beginning be matched now by your giving. Give in proportion to what you have. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"12"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"12"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"12"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Whatever you give is acceptable if you give it eagerly. And give according to what you have, not what you don’t have. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"13"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"13"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"13"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Of course, I don’t mean your giving should make life easy for others and hard for yourselves. I only mean that there should be some equality. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"14"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"14"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"14"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Right now you have plenty and can help those who are in need. Later, they will have plenty and can share with you when you need it. In this way, things will be equal. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"15"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"15"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"15"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"As the Scriptures say,\n“Those who gathered a lot had nothing left over, \nand those who gathered only a little had enough.”* \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"16"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"16"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"16"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"But thank God! He has given Titus the same enthusiasm for you that I have. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"17"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"17"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"17"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Titus welcomed our request that he visit you again. In fact, he himself was very eager to go and see you. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"18"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"18"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"18"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"We are also sending another brother with Titus. All the churches praise him as a preacher of the Good News. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"19"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"19"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"19"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"He was appointed by the churches to accompany us as we take the offering to Jerusalem*—a service that glorifies the Lord and shows our eagerness to help. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"20"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"20"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"20"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"We are traveling together to guard against any criticism for the way we are handling this generous gift. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"21"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"21"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"21"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"We are careful to be honorable before the Lord, but we also want everyone else to see that we are honorable. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"22"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"22"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"22"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"We are also sending with them another of our brothers who has proven himself many times and has shown on many occasions how eager he is. He is now even more enthusiastic because of his great confidence in you. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"23"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"23"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"23"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"If anyone asks about Titus, say that he is my partner who works with me to help you. And the brothers with him have been sent by the churches,* and they bring honor to Christ. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"24"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"24"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"8","verse":"24"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"So show them your love, and prove to all the churches that our boasting about you is justified. "},{"marks":[{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"\n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"chapter"}],"object":"leaf","text":"9"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"1"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"I really don’t need to write to you about this ministry of giving for the believers in Jerusalem.* "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"2"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"2"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"2"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"For I know how eager you are to help, and I have been boasting to the churches in Macedonia that you in Greece* were ready to send an offering a year ago. In fact, it was your enthusiasm that stirred up many of the Macedonian believers to begin giving. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"3"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"3"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"3"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"But I am sending these brothers to be sure you really are ready, as I have been telling them, and that your money is all collected. I don’t want to be wrong in my boasting about you. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"4"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"4"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"4"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"We would be embarrassed—not to mention your own embarrassment—if some Macedonian believers came with me and found that you weren’t ready after all I had told them! "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"5"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"5"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"5"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"So I thought I should send these brothers ahead of me to make sure the gift you promised is ready. But I want it to be a willing gift, not one given grudgingly. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"6"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"6"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"6"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Remember this—a farmer who plants only a few seeds will get a small crop. But the one who plants generously will get a generous crop. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"7"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"7"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"7"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"You must each decide in your heart how much to give. And don’t give reluctantly or in response to pressure. “For God loves a person who gives cheerfully.”* "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"8"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"8"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"8"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"And God will generously provide all you need. Then you will always have everything you need and plenty left over to share with others. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"9"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"9"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"9"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"As the Scriptures say, \n“They share freely and give generously to the poor. \nTheir good deeds will be remembered forever.”* \n"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"10"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"10"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"10"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"For God is the one who provides seed for the farmer and then bread to eat. In the same way, he will provide and increase your resources and then produce a great harvest of generosity* in you. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"11"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"11"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"11"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Yes, you will be enriched in every way so that you can always be generous. And when we take your gifts to those who need them, they will thank God. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"12"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"12"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"12"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"So two good things will result from this ministry of giving—the needs of the believers in Jerusalem* will be met, and they will joyfully express their thanks to God. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"13"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"13"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"13"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"As a result of your ministry, they will give glory to God. For your generosity to them and to all believers will prove that you are obedient to the Good News of Christ. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"14"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"14"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"14"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"And they will pray for you with deep affection because of the overflowing grace God has given to you. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"15"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"15"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"9","verse":"15"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Thank God for this gift* too wonderful for words! "}]}]}],"colors":{"total":1045,"black":1045,"red":0,"green":0,"blue":0},"repeatedWords":["have (11)","give (9)","God (11)","giving (8)","churches (7)","has (6)","need (6)","believers (6)","many (5)","brothers (5)","our (5)","gift (5)","all (5)","also (5)","want (5)","Titus (5)","don’t (5)","us (4)","generous (4)","help (4)"],"sources":{"The Narrator":{"words":1045,"color":"black"}},"id":"S333"}